99-hdmi_sound.rules was based on: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/PulseAudio/Examples#Automatically_switch_audio_to_HDMI

To make the change effective don't forget to reload the udev rules:
udevadm control --reload-rules
(or even reboot system)


